cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this corpus, please cite it as below."
title: "Convergent Form, Divergent Voice II — Corpus"
abstract: >
  A research data corpus of free-form contemplative writing samples from
  49 large language models across 226 model-route cells, with explicit
  per-provider routing pinning for nine multi-provider open-weights
  models. Companion data for the v2 series of Convergent Form, Divergent
  Voice papers (drift, routing, product-tier).
